{"tid":1699762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中彈急救員 大腿皮植背部 警暴身心留痕","createTime":"2019-11-08T07:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T07:53:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"69dab25e03e94154d9fbf2fe5330357f5911ec7b","tid":1699762,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:07:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191108/QJHXGDCVZ2QN4YKET57BKWXWW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191108%2FQJHXGDCVZ2QN4YKET57BKWXWW4%2F&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUhYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=3ac2c0ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191108%2FQJHXGDCVZ2QN4YKET57BKWXWW4%2F&h=e3bb0065\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191108/QJHXGDCVZ2QN4YKET57BKWXWW4/</a><br />\n<br />\n中彈急救員<br />\n大腿皮植背部 警暴身心留痕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【三級燒傷】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】上周六的港島警民衝突中，一名18歲義務急救員被防暴警員手擲催淚彈燒傷背部，昨晨接受四小時植皮手術，成功將右大腿一幅表皮移植至背部。傷者手術前向《蘋果》稱兒時以當警察為志願，17歲考取急救資格為投考警員鋪路，豈料反送中運動令他認清警暴的可惡，決心上前線救人。當日催淚彈在其頭頂爆開，跌入其上衫與背脊間，高溫釀成二至三級燒傷，他形容「痛得好恐怖」。他目前「食五、六粒止痛藥先敢去沖涼同洗傷口」，但他無悔上前線救人，強調「出手係一個責任，有任何需要幫助嘅情況，我都會出場」。<br />\n<br />\n記者：姜偉康<br />\n<br />\n就讀樹仁大學輔導及心理系的18歲學生阿仁（化名），上周六與隊友在港島示威活動中擔任義務急救員，傍晚6時許身處銅鑼灣波斯富街的電車站，被警員擲出一枚手投式催淚彈燒傷背部，皮膚當場被燒至熏黑脫皮。他至今仍留醫瑪麗醫院燒傷中心，昨早7時許開始接受四小時植皮手術，至中午手術成功，視乎康復進度再決定下一步治療方式。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/hGtTK_NjdNlxrwrx20uwFjUYyJg=/802x1414/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/HMRF565Z7GZ7AA3EWKFVXD2FOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FhGtTK_NjdNlxrwrx20uwFjUYyJg%3D%2F802x1414%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FHMRF565Z7GZ7AA3EWKFVXD2FOY.jpg&h=c3164966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n義務急救員阿仁背部及手部燒傷，但無悔上前線救人。姜偉康攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/7UA3er1yrqPM-v83VLs-gL8qtuE=/802x1069/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/SMEAH5SE3U2O5EZJ6REOV6CHCI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F7UA3er1yrqPM-v83VLs-gL8qtuE%3D%2F802x1069%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FSMEAH5SE3U2O5EZJ6REOV6CHCI.jpg&h=f20988e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿仁左手兩隻手指曾夾走高溫催淚彈，造成二級燒傷。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/gJOmEGkpcoVAEwvOIluLU2dAXFk=/802x1069/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/CYATM5KX7PS65IEXCNWPVG3WYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FgJOmEGkpcoVAEwvOIluLU2dAXFk%3D%2F802x1069%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FCYATM5KX7PS65IEXCNWPVG3WYY.jpg&h=031a9448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傷者背部有二級和三級燒傷，須進行植皮手術。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n背部及兩指嚴重燒傷<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：民間「和你宵」建黃色經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n阿仁左手兩隻手指包着繃帶，背部敷上一大塊紗布，前晚在醫院講述事發經過。他憶述當日下午3時起充當義務急救員，先後遊走維園、炮台山至銅鑼灣，傍晚6時許身處波斯富街的有蓋電車站內，當時無戴防毒面罩，背向防暴警員提醒記者小心，未幾在頭頂上方聽到一聲爆響，有物體攝入其身穿的polo恤與背脊之間，他本能用左手食指及中指夾出催淚彈，造成背部及手指嚴重燒傷。「之前（催淚彈）係煙霧狀，頂多刺激皮膚，嗰日跌入背脊，有股噴射感覺，有人更話見到火光，相信係國產催淚彈先造到呢個效果」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原為投考警察學急救<br />\n<br />\n阿仁其後確診背部有0.5%三級燒傷及2至3%二級燒傷，兩隻手指有二級燒傷，需定期洗傷口。他形容過去留醫六天度日如年，「瞓低起身都痛，每日洗傷口同沖涼都好痛，痛到成個人孿起，要食五至六粒止痛藥先敢去做」，預計至少數星期至個多月才能復原。<br />\n<br />\n義務工作本來已是無償服務，現換來終生留痕，阿仁指這種使命感不是生而有之，諷刺的是源於傷害他的警察：「細個志願做警察，以為係好職業，可以幫到巿民，17歲學急救，諗住幫到人，仲以為考警察有優勢。」然而今年6月以來反佔中運動，他以聖約翰救傷隊救護員身份出席集會，但之後警務處屢次拒絕批出不反對通知書，聖約翰救傷隊無法出動，他遂化身義務急救員繼續工作。「直播見到有人受傷，發現警察未必可以幫到巿民，決定用急救技術去幫返有需要嘅人」。他仍希望康復後重回前線出力，現透過民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇協助，不排除稍後向投訴警察課投訴，或透過民事訴訟討回公道。"},{"pid":"e0d8a376e0b818c148e2fb117860e515adb21d7e","tid":1699762,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:09:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ef5b2f679a666b60fc289fa2fcf1f58441662d7","tid":1699762,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990ac86ab38c0bfbbc228f15a49b597ea2f0a935","tid":1699762,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:15:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133f5377698ceadbf658ae0ef6ddfd6c8b3eef8a","tid":1699762,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:15:46.000Z","msg":"屌 好似仲傷過隻聖水狗"},{"pid":"e8180230091a9e28faf9001776214a4cc222dc08","tid":1699762,"uid":180124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"133f5377698ceadbf658ae0ef6ddfd6c8b3eef8a","tid":1699762,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:15:46.000Z","msg":"屌 好似仲傷過隻聖水狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:19:26.000Z","msg":"明顯啦"},{"pid":"2f1405f51045b0d05570d6b6ddbd41d523974c28","tid":1699762,"uid":38533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:21:14.000Z","msg":"睇見都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0f6e2b79919bdadd6edadba02148e97ea4dc48","tid":1699762,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:21:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c77e7be841730d891862d68f4421bfabc591d249","tid":1699762,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:21:35.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5add5a3691a9bda5a614f392a670a8e9d73ff666","tid":1699762,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:24:47.000Z","msg":"(請承認自己的無能) 幫全香港被罷工的事前準備細節及討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1699780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1699780</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ba246768a1b0cb7ac1697b2193e27ce4001858a0","tid":1699762,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"隔熱手套有無用? 掟撚返比班仆街狗"},{"pid":"ece19b23796ee08a6dba57cd6eef821f61ddf18f","tid":1699762,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f085ead5de78bee3f7e6dc4f83cf87102d0d3e80","tid":1699762,"uid":313635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:26:54.000Z","msg":"香港靠你班暴徒區區開花食撚得屎啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1699701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1699701</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0637f5ecaf14cf5963a8514cc76bf3bcd8f2e671","tid":1699762,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e446d0310ee4b8d11697d1e2ccbfaf153c90567d","tid":1699762,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba246768a1b0cb7ac1697b2193e27ce4001858a0","tid":1699762,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"隔熱手套有無用? 掟撚返比班仆街狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"路政署話230度以上先會可以將佢哋啲油漆黃色燒到變青色"}]}